description:
@mcp.prompt for 'who got my money this month'. Args: budget_id, period: Literal['this_month','last_month','last_90d','ytd']. 

Output: prompt text directing the model to call spending_by_payee tool (Epic 5) with sensible top-N, then format a markdown ranking + period-over-period delta.

Depends on Epic 5 (spending_by_payee tool).

@mcp.tool wrapping GET /budgets/{id}/categories/{cat_id}/transactions.

Args: budget_id, category_id, since_date (optional). Returns markdown table same shape as get_transactions.

Answers 'show me everything that hit Groceries this month'.

@mcp.tool wrapping POST /budgets/{id}/transactions/import. Triggers YNAB to re-pull from connected bank accounts.

Args: budget_id. Returns: list of newly imported transaction ids.

Used after reconnecting an account or when transactions seem stale. Annotation: IDEMPOTENT_MUTATING_TOOL (server-side dedupes by import_id).
